messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Enemy communication intercepted. Security level elevated.

A summary has been copied and printed to all communications consoles.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Good morning, Folks, This is the Central Wrestling Federation, Your station has been picked for a big MMA Fighting Event, Whoever beats Dickhole the Professional Wrestler gets the grand prize, So come on down to the Bar and mark your territory!

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Central Wrestling Federation Medium-Priority Update

Based on the communications traffic on your station, we believe that one of the station's bots/animals has developed lizard level intelligence, and the ability to communicate.
